{"tid":202489,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"斯里蘭卡垃圾山崩塌  毀逾百家園16人命喪","createTime":"2017-04-15T14:01:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-15T14:22:36.000Z","uid":87337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"8efa5b2e56f2f230db70008fafd1d89957182beb","tid":202489,"uid":87337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:01:51.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170415/mobile/bknint-20170415150802935-0415_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170415%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20170415150802935-0415_17011_001.html&d=Vmg9VhgMmKCDk1oLDtgP7u9M5Ue6CDmcYDZznX2R1Ws%3D&h=6c060640\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170415/mobile/bknint-20170415150802935-0415_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n91米垃圾山倒塌 死左好多細路 <br />\n當地慶祝緊傳統新年 本來好開心<br />\n但就喺一夜 因為個垃圾山 化為烏有<br />\n<br />\n其實點解會有垃圾山呢樣野？<br />\n又冇壓縮 又冇分類<br />\n垃圾山 唔單止倒塌既時候會傷亡慘重<br />\n平日附近既環境都一定烏煙瘴氣 <br />\n惹昆蟲 空氣差 衛生差<br />\n<br />\n當地政府喺處理垃圾嗰方面知識貧乏？<br />\n再講 點解一日會有咁多垃圾？<br />\n<br />\n教育同文明 <br />\n真係好緊要<br />\n<br />\n雖然香港比斯里蘭卡識得處理垃圾<br />\n但香港人繼續日日瘋狂浪費 製造垃圾<br />\n遲早一日 都好似斯里蘭卡咁<br />\n垃圾同人 爭地方住<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n有冇喺呢方面多啲知識既巴絲打一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f10faf69bf3619c09b009fcbf33dceec2f446c1","tid":202489,"uid":53794,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:06:53.000Z","msg":"俾錢第三世界接受垃圾咪得"},{"pid":"20bb16163925e91dd49f976dc56c10bd795d199f","tid":202489,"uid":4525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:11:09.000Z","msg":"無錢點解決"},{"pid":"6d04aee5657e9744529493e0dd0d298bf5f9bcc0","tid":202489,"uid":87337,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:15:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>無錢點解決</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n的確係<br />\nIt's all about money"},{"pid":"28bbf3a002b06a948c9de5b467eb241c4869b775","tid":202489,"uid":76410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:19:28.000Z","msg":"係香港天水圍都有座非法泥頭山"},{"pid":"b98e9e0024d78e6095b2fbb515ba34125e422f1c","tid":202489,"uid":76410,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-15T14:22:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>係香港天水圍都有座非法泥頭山</blockquote><br />\n當然唔會好似斯里蘭卡同上年深圳咁嚴重<br />\n但可以反映欠管理嘅垃圾堆同山泥傾瀉同樣嚴重"}]}